text = "Because the result of a modulo operation never goes above a certain amount, we can easily use it to simulate dice rolling.

The function [code]randi()[/code] returns a random whole number. We can limit the range of the number by using the modulo operation. 

Because we use the modulo operation on a random number, the result is also random."
